.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, orange, pink, mauve, apricot
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes red is between the person who likes mauve and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person who likes green##1
8. the person who likes pink is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the person who likes orange is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Color          | pink | red | mauve | green | apricot | blue      | orange  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

