.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
City: edinburgh, nizza, colone, miami, marseilles, hannover, hamburg
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person traveling to miami##2
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| City   | hamburg | marseilles | edinburgh | nizza   | miami | colone | hannover |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

