.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
7 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, canasta, monopoly, backgammon, poker, snooker
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, cycling, lacrosse, parkour, rowing, snowboarding
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person playing chess##2
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the person playing poker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Game     | backgammon | chess | monopoly | poker | mah-jongg | canasta     | snooker |
| Sport   | cycling   | lacrosse    | snowboarding    | parkour      | climbing  | badminton | rowing |

