.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, freelancer, manager, entrepreneur, lawyer, social-worker, police-officer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the lawyer##1
 2. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the manager is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 6. the architect is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the architect##1
 8. the social-worker is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the lawyer##2
10. the manager is on the left of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Job   | architect | freelancer    | entrepreneur | manager   | social-worker | police-officer    | lawyer |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

