 6. the person who likes white is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes red##2
 7. the dressmaker is on the right of the police-officer##1
 8. the accountant is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 9. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes red and the person who likes lilac##2
11. the photographer is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
