.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, disaster, horror, romance, satire, thriller
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, soul, techno, punk, funk, rock, country
1. the person watching action movies is the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is between the fan of country and the fan of funk##2
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the fan of classical is in the middle##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of funk##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the fan of country is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | satire | romance | disaster | thriller  | action |
| Music-Genre     | techno | punk | funk   | classical     | country    | soul | rock   |

