The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, gardening, hiking, magic-tricks, photography, singing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
8. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's hobby is photography##2
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Sport   | skiing  | snowboarding       | rowing         | sailing         | golf   | lacrosse        | tennis |
| Hobby      | singing | gardening | board-games | magic-tricks | cooking | photography | hiking  |

